title: Ghazali Butt wins PP-146 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Ghazali Saleem Butt of the Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz (PML-N) has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-146 Lahore-II by securing 30,587 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was independent candidate Junaid Razzaq, who bagged 28,515 votes.
Votersâ€™ turn-out remained 38.31%.
